HIGHLY POSEABLE WITH PREMIUM DETAILING: G.I. Joe Classified Series Desert Commando Snake Eyes action figure features premium detailing and articulation for poseability to create dynamic dioramas (some poses may require additional support)

body.description: G.I. Joe is a highly skilled, on-demand, special operations force of men and women from around the globe. tasked with defending the world from Cobra, a ruthless criminal organization bent on total domination. The brave members of G.I. Joe are prepared to seek out Cobra in any environment on the planet. From hostile jungles to ice-clad arctic peaks…wherever there’s trouble, G.I. Joe is there. New to the G.I. Joe Classified Series line, Desert Commando Snake Eyes comes ready for adventure, with multiple points of articulation for high poseability. This Desert Commando Snake Eyes figure contains 9 character-inspired accessories including backpack, scabbard, 2 swords, knife, removable grenade bandolier, and two weapon accessories with an interchangeable suppressor; plus a footlocker to stow all his gear! Geared up for a desert mission, Snake Eyes is ready to blow in like a sirocco and vanish without a trace. G.I. Joe and all related characters are trademarks of Hasbro.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: G.I. Joe Classified Series | Desert Commando Snake Eyes Code Name: SNAKE EYES File Name: Classified Birthplace: Classified Subject was Ranger qualified and served in Long Range Recon Patrols in Southeast Asia. Left the service to study mystic martial arts with the same Ninja family that produced Storm Shadow. Snake-Eyes was living an ascetic existence alone in the High Sierras with a pet wolf named Timber when he was recruited for the G.I. Joe Team. Snake Eyes is proficient in 12 different unarmed fighting systems (Karate, Kung-Fu, Jujitsu) and is highly skilled in the use of edged weapons. Has received extensive training in mountaineering, underwater demolitions, jungle, desert and arctic survival, and some form of holistic medicine. Qualified Expert: All small arms. "The man is a total mystery, but he's real good at his job, heck, he's the best."

Product Features: Yo Joe! The G.I. Joe Classified Series line of action figures captures the pulse-pounding excitement of G.I. Joe in a 6-inch scale. And it’s all showcased in collectible display-worthy packaging. All Geared Up Affix the peg of the sheath to his backpack to allow Snake Eyes to stow his large sword. Strap on or remove his grenade bandolier to customize your poses. Hidden in Plain Sight The Desert Commando Snake Eyes figure is ideal for desert diorama displays, camouflaging amidst sandy terrain. Pose him poised to strike enemy Cobra figures with deadly precision.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A true classic American Hero
reviews.reviewText: A great figure already released multiple times through other figures as this is the classic example of re-releasing old molds through new colors and tools. The commando head on the original Ninja body with the commando weapons and previous accessories from both figures besides timber, the rifle, and SMG which is good for $25-($17 right now)It reminds me of being a kid with cool figures coming in different colors and looks they probably didn’t have but still looked awesome for me enough to get them. For full price it’s a damn good figure but for a retool I’d say wait a bit for the price to be knocked down like I did
